15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 74 O.S. 2021, Section 2276.1, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 2276.1. A. There is hereby created a trust fund to be
19 known as the “Oklahoma State Park Trust Fund”. The Oklahoma Tourism
20 and Recreation Commission shall be the trustees of the Trust Fund
21 trust fund.
22 B. 1. The Commission may utilize five percent (5%) of the
23 principal of the Trust Fund trust fund annually to:
